article.headline: Bryant 70, UC Davis 63
article.story: SAN DIEGO -- Corey Maynard had 19 points and six rebounds and Bryant scored the last seven points of the game in a 70-63 victory over UC Davis in the Basketball Travelers Classic on Saturday. Alex Francis scored 16 points, Frankie Dobbs 12 and Claybrin McMath 10 for the Bulldogs (1-1). Maynard and Francis made layups, and Francis hit two free throws and Dobbs one during the final 4:23. The Aggies (0-2) missed seven shots during that stretch, six from behind the 3-point line. Josh Ritchart led UC Davis with 21 points. Ryan Sypkens had 12 points and seven rebounds, and Ryan Howley scored 11 points.
